  "img": "icons/magic/earth/projectile-boulder-yellow.webp",
  "name": "Pummelstone",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cause a fist-sized chunk of stone to appear and hurl itself against the spell’s target. Make a ranged spell attack. On a hit, the target takes 1d6 bludgeoning damage and must roll a [[/r d4]] when it makes an attack roll or ability check during its next turn, subtracting the result of the d4 from the attack or check roll.</p><p>The spell’s damage increases by 1d6 when you reach 5th level (2d6), 11th level (3d6), and 17th level (4d6).</p>",
